      <description>What the other people said...&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Snare does have it's uses for pulling though. Like when the creature moves very fast in an indoor zone.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sometimes you'll get a tank that's very slow to tag, and snaring the creature right before it reaches the group can save your healer a bit of mana.&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
