      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;snare pulling sucks regardless of class [not talking about&amp;nbsp;snare splitting.&amp;nbsp; Im talking about the act of snaring&amp;nbsp;just to bring it to camp]&amp;nbsp; mem lull and pell when pulling at those levels.&amp;nbsp; lull to your satisfaction then pull with pell.&amp;nbsp; Thats what i did.&amp;nbsp; You can do what ever you want but snaring on a pull should only be done when your scared of something or want to stagger something.&amp;nbsp; But generally speaking bards mez when they want to stagger a pull so thats not really your thing =)&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Keep in mind you can always hit it with snare/slow when its next to camp.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
